parameters.name: AppName
parameters.description: The name of the application to which the network object belongs.

parameters.name: CurrentPage
parameters.description: The number of the page to return. Default value: **1**.

parameters.name: ImageList
parameters.description: The images of the network object.

parameters.name: Namespace
parameters.description: The namespace to which the network object belongs.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description:
The number of entries to return on each page. Default value: 20. If you leave this parameter empty, 20 entries are returned on each page.

> We recommend that you do not leave this parameter empty.

parameters.name: TagList
parameters.description: The labels specified for the network object.

parameters.name: TargetName
parameters.description: The name of the network object.

parameters.name: TargetType
parameters.description:
The type of the network object. Valid values:

*   IMAGE
